==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[grand]] [[unification]] [[theory]]''' (''plural form'': grand unification theories)
#{{physics}} A theory that unifies the [[weak nuclear force]], [[strong nuclear force]], [[electromagnetic force]] and the [[gravitational force]]

====Synonyms====
*Grand unification, grand unified theory, TOE, theory of everything, GUT.

